title: +150,000 Fonts (TrueType, OpenType, PostScript, Other)
description: Here is a collection of more than 150,000 fonts derived from other collections on Pirate Bay.  List has been pruned to remove duplicate font files by comparing SHA1 hash values.  Duplicate names may appear in the collection, however each font is different in some way as the SHA1 hash values are unique.  List has also been run through a font renaming program so the file names make sense.  Enjoy!
